message.body: Hey kaki it's sofie. Wasn't sure if I was supposed to move my stuff into a common area today to make room for new tenants. Rob had mentioned that i should move into the gallery space ... Do you know anything about that? And I still owe you $150 for the next two weeks. Could I bring it Tuesday would that work for you?
I am here now so I could always just go and get you cash. Obviously forgot my checkbook. Like usual. Wish I could just pay you with my brand new iPhone
Stay where u r, until u move out on the 15th. Yes Tuesday is fine;)
